 The blast hit his hand blowing it off. Makeing Galvatron pull back in pain. 
"Okay guess thats off"" His healing powers inheraited from dark mouse started 
to heal his hand causeing a pure liquid form in the shape of a hand to shoot 
up. It would take hours before he could use it again.. "I would not suggest 
continuesing this confilct. I knew you had this treachorous nature and  LIke 
Like is a loyal soilder of Magmatron and in such will attack you if you 
threaten one of his masters men. You are no match for me no less Me and Like 
Like. Be on your way. No one will take you in you are destron. I have made it 
so your body cannot be reprogramed without your spark being destroyed. Oh and 
one more thing if the device in your spark detect any type of surgery or 
senses any preds around you....boom. Go where you can." To make his point he 
transformed into dragon mode and flew off signaling to Like Like to follow.
